Room: The room is minimalist as are all Novotel so not plush luxury, however it was comfortable, quiet and had obviously recently been refurbished - I wonder if from some of the reviews if only part of the hotel has been refurbished.	I always trust TA reviews and chose Novotel Les Halles because I had good rate as an airline employee and most of the other more characteristic hotels were full but were aware of the problems I could have encountered.